The Australian Government funded CSIRO to develop its Hydrogen Knowledge Centre  (https://research.csiro.au/hydrogenknowledge/) , as

a source of information about Australia’s hydrogen project pipeline, hydrogen FAQs and educational resources and the latest in hydrogen

research. 

