Development of renewable energy in Australia and China: A
comparison of policies and status

, Monica Oliphant b, Eric Jing Hu c

Yaping Hua a, *
a Gansu Natural Energy Research Institute, Gansu Academy of Sciences, Lanzhou, 730046, China
b Immediate Past President International Solar Energy Society (ISES), Adelaide, 5042, Australia
